Algorithm
problem 1 ：
link ： https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/valid-anagram/
solution 1: hash table
class Solution {
public:
    bool isAnagram(string s, string t) {
         if( (t.empty() && !s.empty()) || (s.size() != t.size()) )
             return false;
         map<char,int> sMap,tMap;
         for(int i = 0; i < s.size(); i++){
               sMap[s[i]]++;
         }
         for(int j = 0;j < t.size(); j++){
               tMap[t[j]]++;
         }
         if(sMap.size() != tMap.size())
            return false;
         for(auto it = tMap.begin(); it != tMap.end(); it++){
             if(sMap[(*it).first] != (*it).second )
                return false;
         }
        return true;
    }
};
solution 2: sort
class Solution {
public:
    bool isAnagram(string s, string t) {
        if( (t.empty() && !s.empty()) || (s.size() != t.size()) )
             return false;
        sort(s.begin(),s.end());
        sort(t.begin(),t.end());
        if( s == t )
          return true;
        return false;
    }
};

Review
https://medium.com/netflix-techblog/dblog-a-generic-change-data-capture-framework-69351fb9099b
对于现有CDC（change-data-capture）项目的局限性，Netflix团队开始了DBLog项目的开发，
这个DBLog的主要有如下特性：
	1. Processes captured log events in-order.
	2. Dumps can be taken any time
	3. Interleaves log with dump events, by taking dumps in chunks.
	4. No locks on tables are ever acquired
	5. Supports any kind of output
	6. Designed with High Availability in mind
以及相关的需求：
	• Capturing the full state
	• Triggering repairs at any time.
	• Providing high availability for real-time events. 
	• Minimizing database impact. 
	• Writing events to any output.
	• Supporting Relational Databases.
针对以往CDC项目的局限性，提出的一些方案具有以下限制：
	  1. Stopping log event processing while processing a dump.
	  2. Missing ability to trigger dumps on demand. 
	  3. Blocking write traffic by locking tables. 
      4. Using database specific features.

